{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775888292556,"sessionID":"ses_284d07ab7ffevUqCNRQXbXsLJ0","part":{"id":"prt_d7b301503001BmNmoaWMKJYsNa","messageID":"msg_d7b3003d40015SfmQRWYZzlkft","sessionID":"ses_284d07ab7ffevUqCNRQXbXsLJ0","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_766895594c6c4eb3accdc614","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/tasks.md","content":"# AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n\nModule: pkg/workloadmanager\nLanguage: Go\nSize: L\n\n## 测试任务清单\n\n### 1. 核心配置测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `DefaultConfig()` - 验证默认配置值正确\n- [ ] 测试 `LoadConfig()` - 环境变量的正确加载\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 有效值\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 无效值（错误处理）\n  - [ ] KUBECONFIG 环境变量\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_NAMESPACE 环境变量\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_RESYNC_PERIOD 有效/无效值\n  - [ ] WORKLOAD_MANAGER_DEBUG 环境变量\n  - [ ] 无环境变量时的默认行为\n\n### 2. Server 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `NewClient()` \n  - [ ] kubeconfig 文件路径提供时\n  - [ ] kubeconfig 为空时使用 InClusterConfig\n  - [ ] Kubernetes 配置创建失败时的错误处理\n- [ ] 测试 `NewServer()`\n  - [ ] 成功创建 server 实例\n  - [ ] gin 模式设置（debug/release）\n  - [ ] 依赖注入正确\n- [ ] 测试 `Run()`\n  - [ ] 正常启动流程\n  - [ ] context 取消时的关闭\n  - [ ] HTTP 服务错误处理\n- [ ] 测试 `Shutdown()`\n  - [ ] 优雅关闭验证\n\n### 3. Routes 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/routes_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `SetupRoutes()` - 路由正确注册\n- [ ] 验证所有端点正确绑定\n- [ ] 中间件正确应用\n\n### 4. Handler 测试\n\n#### 4.1 AgentRuntime Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `NewAgentRuntimeHandler()`\n- [ ] 测试 `CreateAgentRuntime()`\n  - [ ] 成功创建 AgentRuntime\n  - [ ] 无效 JSON 请求\n  - [ ] namespace 缺失\n  - [ ] name 缺失\n  - [ ] spec.container.image 缺失\n  - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误（NotFound, Conflict, Invalid）\n- [ ] 测试 `ListAgentRuntimes()`\n  - [ ] 成功返回列表\n  - [ ] namespace 参数验证\n  - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误处理\n- [ ] 测试 `GetAgentRuntime()`\n  - [ ] 成功获取单个资源\n  - [ ] 资源不存在\n  - [ ] 参数验证\n- [ ] 测试 `UpdateAgentRuntime()`\n  - [ ] 成功更新\n  - [ ] name 不匹配错误\n  - [ ] 资源不存在\n- [ ] 测试 `DeleteAgentRuntime()`\n  - [ ] 成功删除\n  - [ ] 资源不存在\n\n#### 4.2 CodeInterpreter Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/code_interpreter_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `NewCodeInterpreterHandler()`\n- [ ] 测试 `CreateCodeInterpreter()`\n  - [ ] 成功创建\n  - [ ] 参数验证（namespace, name, image）\n  - [ ] Kubernetes API 错误\n- [ ] 测试 `ListCodeInterpreters()`\n- [ ] 测试 `GetCodeInterpreter()`\n- [ ] 测试 `UpdateCodeInterpreter()`\n- [ ] 测试 `DeleteCodeInterpreter()`\n\n#### 4.3 Sandbox Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 `NewSandboxHandler()`\n- [ ] 测试 `HandleAgentRuntimeCreate()`\n  - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n  - [ ] 请求体验证\n  - [ ] AgentRuntime 不存在\n  - [ ] sandbox 创建超时\n- [ ] 测试 `HandleCodeInterpreterCreate()`\n  - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n  - [ ] CodeInterpreter 不存在\n  - [ ] 创建失败回滚\n\n#### 4.4 Health Handler (pkg/workloadmanager/handler/health_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `NewHealthHandler()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Health()` - 健康检查端点\n- [ ] 测试 `SetReady()` - 就绪状态设置\n\n### 5. Processor 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/processor/sandbox_processor_test.go)\n\n#### 5.1 辅助函数测试\n- [ ] 测试 `RandString()` - 随机字符串生成\n- [ ] 测试 `GenerateSessionID()` - session ID 生成格式\n\n#### 5.2 Getter 函数测试\n- [ ] 测试 `GetAgentRuntime()`\n  - [ ] 成功获取\n  - [ ] lister 为 nil\n  - [ ] 资源不存在\n- [ ] 测试 `GetCodeInterpreter()`\n  - [ ] 成功获取\n  - [ ] lister 为 nil\n  - [ ] 资源不存在\n\n#### 5.3 Build 函数测试\n- [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxObject()`\n  - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox 对象\n  - [ ] 随机后缀生成\n  - [ ] 标签和注解正确复制\n  - [ ] 容器配置正确转换（command, args, env）\n  - [ ] env 的不同类型处理（value, valueFrom）\n- [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxClaimObject()`\n  - [ ] 成功构建 claim 对象\n  - [ ] 标签正确设置\n- [ ] 测试 `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox()`\n  - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox\n  - [ ] 容器配置正确\n\n#### 5.4 Pod IP 解析测试\n- [ ] 测试 `resolvePodIP()`\n  - [ ] pod 直接通过名称找到\n  - [ ] pod 未运行状态\n  - [ ] pod 无 IP\n  - [ ] 通过 label selector 查找\n  - [ ] 通过 owner reference 匹配\n  - [ ] pod 不存在\n\n#### 5.5 EntryPoint 构建测试\n- [ ] 测试 `BuildEntryPoints()` - 入口点正确构建\n\n#### 5.6 CreateSandbox 测试\n- [ ] 测试 `CreateSandbox()`\n  - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n  - [ ] 创建超时回滚\n  - [ ] pod 等待超时\n  - [ ] warm pool 模式\n\n#### 5.7 回滚测试\n- [ ] 测试 `rollback()` - sandbox 删除回滚\n\n### 6. Reconciler 测试\n\n#### 6.1 Manager 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 `DefaultReconcilerConfig()`\n- [ ] 测试 `NewControllerManager()`\n  - [ ] 成功创建\n  - [ ] 客户端配置（QPS, Burst）\n  - [ ] context 初始化\n- [ ] 测试 `AddReconciler()`\n- [ ] 测试 `SetupEventRecorder()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Start()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Shutdown()`\n- [ ] 测试 getter 方法\n- [ ] 测试 `CalculateBackoff()` - 退避算法\n- [ ] 测试 `MapObjectReference()` - 对象引用映射\n\n#### 6.2 AgentRuntime Reconciler 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 `NewAgentRuntimeReconciler()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Run()`\n- [ ] 测试 `processNextWorkItem()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Reconcile()`\n  - [ ] AgentRuntime 不存在\n  - [ ] 删除时间戳设置（资源删除中）\n  - [ ] sandbox pod 创建成功\n  - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（可重试错误）\n  - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（不可重试错误）\n  - [ ] 状态更新成功\n  - [ ] 状态更新失败\n- [ ] 测试 `getAgentRuntime()`\n- [ ] 测试 `reconcileDeletion()`\n- [ ] 测试 `reconcileSandboxPod()`\n  - [ ] pod 不存在时创建\n  - [ ] pod 存在时更新检查\n- [ ] 测试 `getSandboxPod()`\n- [ ] 测试 enqueue 方法\n  - [ ] `EnqueueAgentRuntime()`\n  - [ ] `EnqueueUpdate()`\n  - [ ] `EnqueueDelete()`\n  - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPod()`\n  - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPodUpdate()`\n  - [ ] `EnqueueOwnedPodDelete()`\n\n#### 6.3 Status Updater 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 `NewStatusUpdater()`\n- [ ] 测试 `UpdateAgentRuntimeStatus()`\n  - [ ] 成功更新状态\n  - [ ] 更新失败重试\n\n#### 6.4 Sandbox Processor (Reconciler) 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 `NewSandboxProcessor()`\n- [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxPod()` **[需查看实现]**\n- [ ] 测试 `NeedsUpdate()` **[需查看实现]**\n- [ ] 测试 `UpdateSandboxPod()` **[需查看实现]**\n\n#### 6.5 Owner Reference 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/owner_reference_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 owner reference 相关函数\n\n#### 6.6 Error Handling 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 `IsRetryableError()`\n- [ ] 测试错误常量定义\n\n### 7. Garbage Collector 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `NewGarbageCollector()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Start()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Stop()`\n- [ ] 测试 `gcLoop()`\n- [ ] 测试 `tick()`\n  - [ ] 空闲 sandbox 清理\n  - [ ] 过期 sandbox 清理\n  - [ ] store 错误处理\n- [ ] 测试 `deleteSandbox()`\n  - [ ] 成功删除 Sandbox\n  - [ ] 成功删除 SandboxClaim\n  - [ ] 删除失败（ NotFound 错误）\n  - [ ] 删除失败（其他错误）\n  - [ ] store 删除失败\n- [ ] 测试 `recordAudit()`\n\n### 8. Middleware 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/request_id_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `RequestIDMiddleware()`\n  - [ ] 请求头已存在 X-Request-ID\n  - [ ] 请求头不存在时生成新 UUID\n  - [ ] 响应头正确设置\n  - [ ] context 中设置 request_id\n\n### 9. Response 工具测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go)\n- [ ] 测试 `JSON()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Created()`\n- [ ] 测试 `Error()`\n- [ ] 测试 `ErrorWithID()`\n\n### 10. Types 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types_test.go) **[待创建]**\n- [ ] 测试 `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate()`\n  - [ ] kind 为空\n  - [ ] kind 不是有效类型\n  - [ ] name 为空\n  - [ ] namespace 为空\n  - [ ] 验证通过\n- [ ] 验证常量定义\n\n## 待创建测试文件列表\n1. pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_test.go\n2. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager_test.go\n3. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go\n4. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_updater_test.go\n5. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sandbox_processor_test.go\n6. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/owner_reference_test.go\n7. pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors_test.go\n8. pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types_test.go\n\n## 依赖与 Mock\n- 需要 Mock 的接口：\n  - dynamic.Interface\n  - kubernetes.Interface\n  - corev1lister.PodLister\n  - AgentRuntimeLister\n  - CodeInterpreterLister\n  - store.Store\n  - workqueue.RateLimitingInterface\n  - record.EventRecorder\n\n## 测试覆盖率目标\n- 行覆盖率：≥80%\n- 分支覆盖率：≥70%\n- 关键路径 100% 覆盖\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully